<li>Common mistakes and how to reason through them.</li>
<li>Frequently asked questions from students.</li>
<li>Extra examples that connect theory to implementation.</li>
<li>Debugging notes for notebooks, code, data, and tooling.</li>
<li>Study guidance for assignments, projects, and assessments.</li>
</ul>
<p>Each post should be focused, concrete, and written to help students understand the next step rather than simply giving them an answer.</p>



